\tType\tTime Commitment\tMonthly Cost Founder (You)\tFull-time\t50+ hours/week\tSweat equity Content Writer\tContractor\t60 hours/month\t$3,000 Graphic Designer\tContractor\t20 hours/month\t$1,200 Virtual Assistant\tPart-time\t80 hours/month\t$1,600 Advisory Board (5 experts)\tConsultants\t5 hours/month each\t$2,500 Total Phase 1\t\t\t$8,300/month Phase 2: Small Team (Months 7-12) Add: Community Manager - Part-time ($2,500/month) Email Marketing Specialist - Contractor ($1,800/month) Video Editor - Contractor ($2,000/month) Total Phase 2: $14,600/month Phase 3: Scaling Team (Year 2+) Add: Head of Content - Full-time ($75K salary = $6,250/month) Customer Success Manager - Full-time ($55K salary = $4,583/month) Performance Marketing Manager - Full-time ($70K salary = $5,833/month) Total Phase 3: $31,266/month Product Curation Process (SOP) Product Vetting Workflow Step 1: Initial Screening Research manufacturer/brand reputation Review ingredient list against clinical research Check for FDA warnings or recalls Verify third-party testing (USP, NSF, ConsumerLab) Step 2: Expert Review Submit to relevant advisory board member Request clinical assessment (7-day turnaround) Document expert opinion and rating (1-10 scale) Step 3: Member Testing Recruit 10-20 beta testers from community Provide product at no cost Collect feedback via structured survey Track symptom changes over 30 days Step 4: Final Decision Minimum score: 7/10 from expert + 75% positive member feedback If approved, negotiate commission rate (target: 20-30%) Create product page with expert quote + member testimonials Step 5: Ongoing Monitoring Review member ratings quarterly Remove products with <4 stars Re-evaluate if negative research emerges Product Onboarding Timeline: 30-45 days per product Customer Support Framework Support Channels & Response Times Channel\tHours\tTarget Response Time\tHandled By Email\t24/7 (monitored M-F 9am-6pm EST)\t24 hours\tVA / Customer Success Live Chat\tM-F 10am-4pm EST\t5 minutes\tCustomer Success Community\t24/7 (peer support)\tImmediate (peers)\tCommunity Manager (moderation) Expert Q&A\tMonthly scheduled\tWithin session\tAdvisory Board Phone Support\tBy appointment (Premium only)\t48 hours booking\tFounder / CS Manager Common Support Scenarios & Scripts Scenario 1: Product Recommendation Request Copy Template: \"Based on your [specific symptoms from profile], I recommend starting with [Product A] because [clinical reason]. Many members with similar symptoms report [typical outcome] within [timeframe]. Here's a link to [member testimonials]. Would you like me to send you a discount code?\" Scenario 2: Membership Cancellation Request Copy Step 1: \"I'd love to understand what's not working for you. Is it [access/cost/results/other]?\" Step 2: (Address concern with solution) - Access issues → Platform walkthrough - Cost concerns → Downgrade to lower tier - Results → Connect with expert for personalized plan Step 3: If still canceling → \"Would you consider pausing for 3 months instead? Your progress data will be saved.\" Step 4: Exit survey + \"Stay on free newsletter list\" J. IMPLEMENTATION ROADMAP 12-Month Launch Timeline PHASE 1: FOUNDATION (Months 1-3) Month 1: Infrastructure & Brand Week\tAction Items\tOwner\tBudget\tExpected Ou"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"[Content truncated — view full chat at source URL]"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Source: "},{"type":"link","href":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=62f43528-fe16-4f27-aed3-f1af9beb8a56","children":[{"text":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=62f43528-fe16-4f27-aed3-f1af9beb8a56"}]}]}]
